  <ul class="comments by_rank" >
      
      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="25596927">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/fearntrembling/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1067741-1.jpg" alt="齊" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/25596927/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/25596927/" class="">第200页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/fearntrembling/" class=" " title="齊">齊</a>
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="25596927">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">谕语→论语

中国之弱在于习气太深，文法太密，庸俗之吏多，豪杰之士少。文法者，庸人藉为藏身之固，而胥吏恃为牟利之符。公私以文牍相往来，而毫无实际，人才以资格相限制，而日见消磨。误国家者在一私字，祸天下者在一例字。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2013-04-05 21:30</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                谕语→论语<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div><blockquote><q>中国之弱在于习气太深，文法太密，庸俗之吏多，豪杰之士少。文法者，庸人藉为藏身之固，而胥吏恃为牟利之符。公私以文牍相往来，而毫无实际，人才以资格相限制，而日见消磨。误国家者在一私字，祸天下者在一例字。</q></blockquote>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







